In [20]:
mean1 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==1]['SalePrice'].mean()
std1 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==1]['SalePrice'].std()
nobs1 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==1]['SalePrice'].count()
mean2 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==2]['SalePrice'].mean()
std2 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==2]['SalePrice'].std()
nobs2 = traindf[traindf['GarageCars']==2]['SalePrice'].count()
ttest_ind_from_stats(mean1, std1, nobs1, mean2, std2, nobs2, equal_var=False)
Out[20]:
Ttest_indResult(statistic=-23.263431165660258, pvalue=8.93540934556563e-98)

The t statistic is too large for a significance of 0.05. So, the car space affects the SalePrice significantly.

In [ ]:

A t statistic of 1.38 for a significance of 0.05 means we cannot reject the Null Hypothesis.

In [21]:
#Pool Area. 
#H0: the SalePrice means of two groups are indifferent
#Ha: the SalePrice means of two groups are different
observed_mean_diff = traindf[traindf['PoolArea'] > 0]['SalePrice'].mean() - traindf[traindf['PoolArea'] == 0]['SalePrice'].mean()
print('Observed diff:',observed_mean_diff)
mean_diff = []
for i in range(1000):
    mean_pool = traindf[traindf['PoolArea'] > 0]['SalePrice'].sample(frac=1,replace=True).mean()
    mean_no_pool = traindf[traindf['PoolArea'] == 0]['SalePrice'].sample(frac=1,replace=True).mean()
    mean_diff.append(mean_pool - mean_no_pool)

confidence_interval = np.percentile(mean_diff,[0.025,0.975])
print(confidence_interval)

Observed diff: 107733.90797365058
[-16286.706291      379.99669622]
In [22]:
#Central_Air

observed_mean_diff = traindf[traindf['CentralAir'] == 'Y']['SalePrice'].mean() - traindf[traindf['CentralAir'] == 'N']['SalePrice'].mean()
print('Observed diff:',observed_mean_diff)
mean_diff = []
for i in range(1000):
    mean_Air = traindf[traindf['CentralAir'] == 'Y']['SalePrice'].sample(frac=1,replace=True).mean()
    mean_no_Air = traindf[traindf['CentralAir'] == 'N']['SalePrice'].sample(frac=1,replace=True).mean()
    mean_diff.append(mean_Air - mean_no_Air)

confidence_interval = np.percentile(mean_diff,[0.025,0.975])
print(confidence_interval)

Observed diff: 80922.63620589937
[64130.00969891 68828.49043194]
